{"tid":813781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對面樓有單位做佐民宿","createTime":"2018-09-10T17:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T17:52:02.000Z","uid":23757,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"709f9571b7870d83077884ca3f40db188f901d11","tid":813781,"uid":23757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"一間房兩張碌架床<br />\n十幾個人係哂間房到播歌<br />\n隔成條街都聽到播乜<br />\n講野又大聲<br />\n3 4點起身仲見到間房著哂燈<br />\n係airbnb又唔見有<br />\n<br />\n你話普通民宿都冇咩所謂<br />\n反正唔係我住果棟大廈有<br />\n但你整到成間hostel咁<br />\n仲要冇窗簾<br />\n真係好擾民喎"},{"pid":"dabf556c6ba5b55a93355fb8679459e8bc8e67c8","tid":813781,"uid":18628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af3a22995b5ccdc1d6042bd052cfaa418ce69c7","tid":813781,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db63a90a0d423c4bdbba06da0fbb6ca80f30a1e2","tid":813781,"uid":23757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/014530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F014530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82847983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af3cb1378b10ab0baead1f24dccb71e05cf709f","tid":813781,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db63a90a0d423c4bdbba06da0fbb6ca80f30a1e2","tid":813781,"uid":23757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/014530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F014530_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jp